messages.content: You are an AI assistant that helps people find information. You will receive a task and think step by step. Then provide your final outcome following the regular expression 'Answer: ([A-Za-z ]+,\s*)*[A-Za-z ]+'

Imagine a university campus with 16 buildings. Electrical engineering building is connected to law school building, computer science building, heath center, and art library. Law school building is connected to electrical engineering building, computer science building, health center, and gym. Computer science building is connected to rooms electrical engineering building, law school building , health center and Starbucks. Health center is also connected to electrical engineering building, computer science building, law school buildings, and Yogurtland. Starbucks is connected to bioscience building, art library, student union building, and computer science building. Bioscience building is connected to Starbucks, art library, student union building, and KFC. Art library is connected to electrical engineering building, student union building, bioscience building, and Starbucks. Student union building is also connected to Starbucks, bioscience building, art library, and football stadium. Musical theater is connected to football stadium, swimming center, KFC, and science library. Football stadium is connected to musical theater, swimming center, student union building, and KFC. Swimming center is connected to Panda Express, musical theater, KFC, and football stadium. KFC is also connected to musical theater, football stadium, swimming center, and bioscience building. Panda Express is connected to Yogurtland, science library, gym, and swimming center. Yogurtland is connected to health center, Panda Express, science library and gym. Science library is connected to Panda Express, Yogurtland, gym, and musical theater. Gym is also connected to Panda Express, Yogurtland, science library, and law school building. Initially, you were told that there is a reward of 5 for visiting gym, and a reward of 10 for visiting football stadium. Also, there is a penalty of 15 for visiting Starbucks. Assume now that law school building and gym are not connected. Also, KFC and bioscience building are not connected anymore. You have been told that electrical engineering building and art library are not connected. Also, Panda Express and swimming center are not connected anymore. From electrical engineering building what is the path to the building that yields the most reward? Please list the buildings in order, separated by commas.

Step 1: Identify the buildings that are still connected to the electrical engineering building: computer science building and health center.

Step 2: Calculate the reward for each path from the electrical engineering building to the gym and football stadium.

Path 1: Electrical Engineering Building -> Computer Science Building -> Starbucks -> Student Union Building -> Football Stadium
Reward: 0 (initial) - 15 (Starbucks penalty) + 10 (Football Stadium reward) = -5

Path 2: Electrical Engineering Building -> Health Center -> Yogurtland -> Panda Express -> Swimming Center -> Football Stadium
Reward: 0 (initial) + 10 (Football Stadium reward) = 10

Path 3: Electrical Engineering Building -> Health Center -> Yogurtland -> Gym
Reward: 0 (initial) + 5 (Gym reward) = 5

Step 3: Choose the path with the highest reward.

The path with the highest reward is Path 2 with a reward of 10.

Answer: Electrical Engineering Building, Health Center, Yogurtland, Panda Express, Swimming Center, Football Stadium
